(2, 1, '2014-02-06 10:46:01', '2014-02-06 10:46:01', '<div class="content">\r\n<div class="container_12 ">\r\n<div class="grid_12">\r\n<h3>公司简介</h3>\r\n\r\n本公司由资深会计师、大律师、政府特许移民代理及各类专业商业投资人仕，贸易顾问为阁下提供一系列完善服务。一直以来，本公司协助无数的港澳、台湾、和中国大陆人仕合法移民澳大利亚，具有无数成功的经验。\r\n(本公司的专业人仕会对每一个申请人作出慎重评估，如没有百分百的成功机会，我们是不会接纳你的个案，这是我们一贯的服务宗旨，它促使我们慎重选择条件优异的申请者，以免令申请人蒙受不必要的损失和因被拒签证而留下记录。)\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '关于', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2014-05-14 14:19:43', '2014-05-14 04:19:43', '', 0, 'http://192.168.0.222/southpac/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1, 1, '2014-03-26 06:08:35', '2014-03-26 06:08:35', '[metaslider id=99]\r\n\r\n<div class="page1_block">\r\n<div class="p1_top">\r\n<div class=" container_12">\r\n<div class="grid_12">[sbscrbr_form]</div>\r\n<div class="clear">\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--==============================Content=================================-->\r\n<div class="container_12 p_bot">\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="#"><span>A.</span>免费移民评估</a></h3>\r\n专业顾问将为您进行免费移民评估，针对不同情况给出具体评估结果。\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="#"><span>C.</span>定制移民计划</a></h3>\r\n专业顾问将为您量身定制整套移民方案，确保移民过程的安全可靠。\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="#"><span>B.</span>申请各类学校</a></h3>\r\n不管你是哪类学生，专业留学顾问都会全力协助并精心设计你的学习方案。\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="block1">\r\n<h3><a href="./contact"><span>D.</span><strong class="nowrap">咨询服务</strong></a></h3>\r\n位于悉尼市中心的办事处使您能很方便的找到我们，你可以给我们打电话或者发邮件获得实时的移民信息\r\n<br />\r\n<a class="btn" href="contact">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="container_12 ">\r\n<div class="grid_12">\r\n<blockquote class="bq1">\r\n<div class="grid_3 alpha">\r\n<div class="bq_left"><img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\nPraesent vestibulum aenean nonummy hendrerit mauris. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et mgnis dis parturient montes ascetur ridiculus mus. Nulla dui. Fusce feugiat malesuada odio. Morbi nunc odio gravida at cursus nec luctus a lorem. Maecenas tristique orci ac sem. Duis ultricies pharetra magna onec accumsan malesuada orci. Donec sit amet eros. <img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/quotes.png" />\r\n<div class="bq_bot">\r\n\r\nJohn Cox\r\n<div class="upp">(专业移民顾问)</div>\r\n</div></blockquote>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="grid_12">\r\n<div class="block2">\r\n<h3 class="upp">有问题吗?\r\n<br />\r\n咨询专家</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="c_phone">(02) 9266 0318</div>\r\n<address>\r\n周一到周五\r\n早上9点\r\n到下午5点</address>\r\n<div class="grid_3 fright omega">\r\n\r\n<a href="#" class="livelychatsupport-open chat">在线咨询</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img1.jpg" />\r\n<h3>商务签证</h3>\r\nPraesent vestibulum aeneannonummy hendrerit mauris. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et mgnis dis parturient montes ascetur\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img2.jpg" />\r\n<h3>家庭团聚</h3>\r\nPraesent vestibulum aeneannonummy hendrerit mauris. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et mgnis dis parturient montes ascetur\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img3.jpg" />\r\n<h3>学生签证</h3>\r\nPraesent vestibulum aeneannonummy hendrerit mauris. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et mgnis dis parturient montes ascetur\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grid_3">\r\n<div class="box ">\r\n<div class="maxheight">\r\n<div class="box_inner">\r\n<img alt="" src="../wp-content/themes/southpac/images/page1_img4.jpg" />\r\n<h3>访问签证</h3>\r\nPraesent vestibulum aeneannonummy hendrerit mauris. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et mgnis dis parturient montes ascetur\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="#">更多信息</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '首页', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2014-05-14 14:21:50', '2014-05-14 04:21:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/southpac/?page_id=1', 0, 'page', '', 0),
